          "description": "The Koppelman team is excellent. From the support staff to the technicians, hygienists, and doctors (I've had the pleasure of seeing both Adam and Paul), everyone is dedicated, skilled, and genuinely caring. They take the time to explain things clearly, and I always leave feeling like I'm in good hands. After years of searching for a dental practice I could trust, I'm so grateful my wife referred me here. Highly recommended.",
