          "description": "I've had an outstanding experience with Koppelman Dental! From the moment I arrived, the entire process was smooth and easy. Scheduling was a piece of cake, and communication was clear and effortless throughout.\n\nAdam was incredibly honest, caring, and attentive. The entire staff took the time to explain everything in a straightforward way and made sure I was comfortable at every step. They were also extremely gentle \u2014 easily one of the easiest experiences I've ever had in a dental chair. My teeth have never looked better!\n\nIf you\u2019re looking for a dentist who truly cares about their patients and makes the whole experience stress-free, this is the place. Highly recommend.",
