          "description": "I had such an incredible experience at Dr. Koppleman\u2019s dental office and truly cannot recommend them highly enough. From the moment I walked in, it was clear that this practice is something special. The office is beautiful, modern, and equipped with state-of-the-art technology that immediately makes you feel confident you\u2019re receiving the best possible care. Dr. Koppleman and his son make an outstanding team. They are both extremely knowledgeable, professional, and genuinely caring. What stood out most to me was how thorough they were throughout the entire visit. They took the time to walk me through every step of the process, explaining what they were doing and why, which made me feel comfortable and well informed as a patient.",
